# .dev.vars.example — copy to .dev.vars for local wrangler pages dev
# This file is the Cloudflare equivalent of .env for Pages Functions.
# .dev.vars is read automatically by `wrangler pages dev` and is NOT committed to git.
# Currently unused: the app calls SkipPay directly via NEXT_PUBLIC_SKIPPAY_API_URL.
# Kept for reference if a server-side proxy is added to functions/ in the future.
